sc_cat_item.description: The Prince Flock Christmas tree makes a grand statement in your home and is the perfect tree to complete your Christmas display. It's tall presence and streamlined construction create a regal and princely ambiance that endows your home with the majesty of the Christmas season. With heavily flocked tips, this frosted tree has the appearance of being covered with gentle dusting or fresh powdered snow. This tree is made from flame-retardant material and features a sturdy metal core to keep your tree standing tall and upright.
